snippet: With only 11 percent of Texas voters showing up for the May primaries, even fewer are expected to wield more clout in the coming runoffs.
lead_paragraph: With only 11 percent of Texas voters showing up for the May primaries, even fewer are expected to wield more clout in the coming runoffs.
